+From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
+From: Jung-Kwang Lee <ntoskrnl7@gmail.com>
+Date: Sat, 2 May 2026 23:53:33 +0900
+Subject: feat: allow Electron to handle renderer print requests
+
+Electron needs to decide how to handle renderer-initiated print requests before Chromium enters the blocking print settings path. This adds a narrow browser callback hook for scripted and PDF plugin print requests while preserving Chromium's default behavior by continuing when no embedder handles the request.
+
